  "texts": [
    "However, incorporating traits into AES models can provide explanations and enhance interpretability of AES models.",
    "Since collecting essays is both difficult and costly, exploring techniques to pre-train essay models that can enrich essays with traits can be considered as a future research direction.",
    "In addition to the scarcity of annotated data, there is also a limitation in the availability of data in languages other than English.",
    "There have been few studies that have utilized datasets in languages other than English (Hirao et al. 2020; Song et al. 2020b; He et al. 2022; Song et al. 2020b, b).",
    "Consequently, the availability of more datasets and AES models trained in different languages can help bridge the gap in democratizing AES systems for underrepresented communities and societies."
